				</ukm:Metadata><Secondary><Schedules RestrictExtent="E+W+S" RestrictStartDate="2026-04-06"><Schedule DocumentURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2013/376/schedule/5" IdURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2013/376/schedule/5" NumberOfProvisions="13" id="schedule-5" RestrictStartDate="2022-04-11"><Number>SCHEDULE 5</Number><TitleBlock><Title>Housing costs element for owner-occupiers</Title></TitleBlock><ScheduleBody><Part DocumentURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2013/376/schedule/5/part/1" IdURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2013/376/schedule/5/part/1" NumberOfProvisions="3" id="schedule-5-part-1" RestrictStartDate="2018-04-06"><Number><Strong>PART 1</Strong></Number><Title>General</Title><P1group RestrictStartDate="2013-04-29"><Title>Introduction</Title><P1 DocumentURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2013/376/schedule/5/paragraph/1" IdURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2013/376/schedule/5/paragraph/1" id="schedule-5-paragraph-1"><Pnumber>1</Pnumber><P1para><P2 DocumentURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2013/376/schedule/5/paragraph/1/1" IdURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2013/376/schedule/5/paragraph/1/1" id="schedule-5-paragraph-1-1"><Pnumber>1</Pnumber><P2para><Text>This Schedule contains provisions about claimants to whom regulation 26(3) applies.</Text></P2para></P2><P2 DocumentURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2013/376/schedule/5/paragraph/1/2" IdURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2013/376/schedule/5/paragraph/1/2" id="schedule-5-paragraph-1-2"><Pnumber>2</Pnumber><P2para><Text>Claimants who fall within sub-paragraph (1) are referred to in this Schedule as  “<Term id="term-owner-occupiers">owner-occupiers</Term>” (and references to  “joint owner-occupiers” are to joint claimants to whom regulation 26(3) applies).</Text></P2para></P2><P2 DocumentURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2013/376/schedule/5/paragraph/1/3" IdURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2013/376/schedule/5/paragraph/1/3" id="schedule-5-paragraph-1-3"><Pnumber>3</Pnumber><P2para><Text>Part 2 of this Schedule sets out an exception to section 11(1) of the Act for certain owner-occupiers in whose case an award of universal credit is not to include an amount of housing costs element calculated under this Schedule.</Text></P2para></P2><P2 DocumentURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2013/376/schedule/5/paragraph/1/4" IdURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2013/376/schedule/5/paragraph/1/4" id="schedule-5-paragraph-1-4"><Pnumber>4</Pnumber><P2para><Text>Part 3 of this Schedule provides for a qualifying period that is to elapse before an amount of housing costs element calculated under this Schedule may be included in an owner-occupier's award of universal credit.</Text></P2para></P2><P2 DocumentURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2013/376/schedule/5/paragraph/1/5" IdURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2013/376/schedule/5/paragraph/1/5" id="schedule-5-paragraph-1-5"><Pnumber>5</Pnumber><P2para><Text>Part 4 provides for the calculation of the amount of housing costs element to be included under this Schedule in an owner-occupier's award of universal credit.</Text></P2para></P2></P1para></P1></P1group></Part></ScheduleBody></Schedule></Schedules></Secondary></Legislation>